description: The fund seeks to match, at the end of the outcome period, the share price returns of the SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust (the underlying ETF), up to a specified upside cap, while providing a buffer against the first 10% of underlying ETF losses. The cap and the buffer will be reduced after taking into account management fees and other fund fees and expenses.
name: AllianzIM U.S. Large Cap 6 Month Buffer10 Apr/Oct ETF
